This document provides the detailed information about the Performance framework.

This project runs on gradle and can extend it to Maven as well incase if we need to switch it. The performance framework is
built on Gatling which is Netty based Aka framework and extensively used for Microservices testing.

Steps to run the Performance framework :

1) Download or Clone the Performance framework code base
2) Navigate to framework directory and run the below gradle command to trigger the Perf tests
         
         gradlew <<taskname>>
         Ex: gradlew incaLoadTest

